      "en": "Volume 45 Book of Later Tang 21: Emperor Min Annals 1",
      "raw": "卷四十五 唐書21: 閔帝本紀 Volume 45 Book of Later Tang 21: Emperor Min Annals 1"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 157,
    "translatedCount": 0,
